/b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=egelmex\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n103\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://geeklife.in.ua/\"><img src=\"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/1715850?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Alex Kucherenko</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=AlexTiTanium\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n104\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://l4sh.github.io\"><img src=\"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/4382808?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Luis Salazar</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=l4sh\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n105\t  </tr>\n106\t  <tr>\n107\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/migonzalvar\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/928566?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Miguel Gonzalez</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=migonzalvar\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n108\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://bitquant.ddns.net:82/\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/2908185?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Joseph Wang</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=joequant\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n109\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/fixmycode\"><img src=\"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/705903?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Pablo Albornoz</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=fixmycode\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n110\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/praveenbm5\"><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/507203?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Praveen Baratam</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=praveenbm5\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n111\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/PLanB2008\"><img src=\"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/26460239?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Andreas Till</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=PLanB2008\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n112\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/zysyl\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/631895?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Roman</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=zysyl\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n113\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://pnijhara.me\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/40136154?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Prajjwal Nijhara</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=pnijhara\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n114\t  </tr>\n115\t  <tr>\n116\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://nailuj.net\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/17853630?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Julian B</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=nailujx86\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n117\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://stackoverflow.com/story/catrielmuller\"><img src=\"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/2272323?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Catriel Müller</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=catrielmuller\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n118\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/UnicronNL\"><img src=\"https://avatars1.githubusercontent.com/u/1267745?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Kim</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=UnicronNL\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n119\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://www.daniel-schulz-software.de\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/8694700?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Daniel Schulz</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=daniel-schulz\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n120\t    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/dendilz\"><img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/33727631?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>dendilz</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=dendilz\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n121\t  </tr>\n122\t</table>\n123\t\n124\t<!-- markdownlint-restore -->\n125\t<!-- prettier-ignore-end -->\n126\t\n127\t<!-- ALL-CONTRIBUTORS-LIST:END -->\n128\t\n129\tThis project follows the [all-contributors](https://github.com/all-contributors/all-contributors) specification. Contributions of any kind welcome!\n130\t\n131\t# Contributing\n132\t\n133\tHelpers are welcome ! There are many ways to help in Ajenti Project : \n134\t\n135\t  * [Translations](https://docs.ajenti.org/en/latest/man/contributing.html)\n136\t  * [Plugin development](https://docs.ajenti.org/en/latest/dev/intro.html)\n137\t  * [Core development](https://docs.ajenti.org/en/latest/dev/intro-core.html)\n138\t\n139\t## Roadmap\n140\t\n141\tActually big changes are planned and under development. A global roadmap is : \n142\t\n143\t  * <s>Migrating to Python3\n144\t  * Migrating to [python-socketio](https://github.com/miguelgrinberg/python-socketio)\n145\t  * Implement better API REST with @get, @post ... decorators</s>\n146\t  * Migrating from AngularJS to Angular 13 (work in progress): \n147\t      * plugins core and dashboard are almost done, but there's a lot of work to migrate all other plugins. \n148\t      * This work take actually place in the branch [ajenti-3-dev](https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/tree/ajenti-3-dev) and the new plugins are stored in the directory [plugins-new](https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/tree/ajenti-3-dev/plugins-new)\n149\t      * The documentation is located at https://docs.ajenti.org/en/ajenti-3-dev/index.html\n150\t  * Add a lot of new plugins: once the migration to Angular done, we can add a lot of plugins to manage services on the server ( like apache2, nginx, postfix, etc ... ).\n151\t  * Migrating to [asyncio](https://docs.python.org/3/library/asyncio.html): concept tested, but migration not really started.\n152\t"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"d5f05358-9f10-4a0b-9283-5878122c41c0","uuid":"709648f5-0871-4baf-aa12-2638fb68079c","timestamp":"2026-04-08T20:24:00.309Z","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/workspace/README.md","content":"[![Logo](docs/img/Logo.png)](https://ajenti.org/)\n\nAjenti is a Linux & BSD modular server admin panel. Ajenti 2 provides a new interface and a better architecture, developed with [Python3](https://www.python.org/) and [AngularJS](https://angularjs.org/).\n\n<p align=\"center\">\n    <a href=\"https://crowdin.net/project/ajenti\">\n        <img src=\"https://badges.crowdin.net/ajenti/localized.svg\" alt=\"Badge Crowdin\" />\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/graphs/contributors\">\n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/contributors/ajenti/ajenti?label=Contributors\" alt=\"Badge Contributors\" />\n    </a>\n    <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/LICENSE\"> \n        <img src=\"https://img.shields.io/github/license/ajenti/ajenti?label=License\" alt=\"Badge License\" />\n    </a>\n</p>\n\n----\n\n# Feature highlights\n\n* **Easy installation** : Ajenti 2 can be easy installed [with pip and the provided script](https://docs.ajenti.org/en/latest/man/install.html#installing).\n\n* **Existing configuration** : Picks up your current configuration and works on your existing system as-is, without any preparation.\n\n* **Caring** : Does not overwrite your config files, options and comments. All changes are non-destructive.\n\n* **Batteries included** : Includes lots of plugins for system and software configuration, monitoring and management.\n\n* **Extensible** : Ajenti 2 is easily extensible using Python. Plugin development is a quick and pleasant with Ajenti APIs. [Write your first plugin](https://docs.ajenti.org/en/latest/dev/intro.html#your-first-plugin).\n\n* **Modern** : Pleasant to look at, satisfying to click and accessible anywhere from tablets and mobile.\n\n* **Lightweight** : Small memory footprint and CPU usage. Runs on low-end machines, wall plugs, routers and so on.\n\n----\n\n# Screenshots\n\n<table align=\"center\">\n    <tr>\n        <td align=\"center\">\n            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-login.png\">\n                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-login.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Login\" width=\"300px\" />\n            </a>\n        </td>\n        <td align=\"center\">\n            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-dashboard.png\">\n                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-dashboard.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Dashboard\" width=\"300px\" /> \n            </a>\n        </td>\n        <td align=\"center\">\n            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-settings.png\"> \n                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-settings.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Settings\" width=\"300px\" />\n            </a>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n    <tr>\n        <td align=\"center\">\n            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-plugins.png\"> \n                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-plugins.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Plugins\" width=\"300px\" /> \n            </a>\n        </td>\n        <td align=\"center\">\n            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-systemd.png\"> \n                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-systemd.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Systemd\" width=\"300px\" />\n            </a> \n        </td>\n        <td align=\"center\">\n            <a href=\"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/ajenti/ajenti/master/docs/img/rd-terminal.png\"> \n                <img src=\"docs/img/rd-terminal.png\" alt=\"Screenshot Ajenti Terminal\" width=\"300px\" /> \n            </a>\n        </td>\n    </tr>\n</table>\n\nSee https://docs.ajenti.org for more information\n\n----\n\n# Contributors ✨\n\nThanks goes to these wonderful people ([emoji key](https://allcontributors.org/docs/en/emoji-key)):\n\n<!-- ALL-CONTRIBUTORS-LIST:START - Do not remove or modify this section -->\n<!-- prettier-ignore-start -->\n<!-- markdownlint-disable -->\n<table>\n  <tr>\n    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://www.unpeud.info\"><img src=\"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/10401079?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Kientz Arnaud</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=kiarn\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"https://github.com/DmZ\"><img src=\"https://avatars2.githubusercontent.com/u/222974?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Dmitry Zamaruev</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=DmZ\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://dierz.pro\"><img src=\"https://avatars3.githubusercontent.com/u/7171587?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Ivlev Denis</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=ivlevdenis\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://bryukh.com\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/343120?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Valentin Bryukhanov</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://github.com/ajenti/ajenti/commits?author=Bryukh\" title=\"Code\">💻</a></td>\n    <td align=\"center\"><a href=\"http://kstep.me\"><img src=\"https://avatars0.githubusercontent.com/u/28537?v=4?s=75\" width=\"75px;\" alt=\"\"/><br /><sub><b>Konstantin Stepanov</b></sub></a><br /><a href=\"https://gi